:{{DIcon|Talk}} Have you always been this pretty?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119103-->
::'''Xikui:''' Oh, that sweet tongue. I wonder how many have been struck down by your glibness, {{MC|f=young lady|m=young man}}?
::'''Xikui:''' Then again, I've always been confident in my looks, which is why I believe your words are sincere. Thank you, and you are very cute too, totally my style.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} About work...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119116-->
::'''Xikui:''' Stop asking about what I do in detail. I'm not going to report my work to someone other than Madam Yukong.
::'''Xikui:''' But I'll tell you a principle I stick to at work: Leaving work on time. Work with maximum efficiency while at work, but the moment I punch out, I turn work mode off.
::'''Xikui:''' Just look around the Sky-Faring Commission &mdash; many love working overtime to prove their efforts. They refuse to get off on time, preferring to dawdle away till late at night. They even think themselves hardworking.
::'''Xikui:''' Me? I'm different. I'll finish up my tasks in a jiffy, and I'm gone when it's time to leave. "Leaving on time" and "sleeping early" are a girl's best friends to looking good.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} About Madam Yukong...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119121-->
::'''Xikui:''' Madam Yukong? She's the best boss I've ever met. You've only seen what she's like when she's working: Strict and serious. She's actually quite adorable in private.
::'''Xikui:''' I've even received dresses gifted by Madam Yukong. I have to say, her taste is impeccable. I frequently wear those dresses of hers when I go out.
::'''Xikui:''' Also, my looks regularly invite trouble from persistent men who don't know their place. It's times like these when Madam Yukong is so dependable.
::'''Xikui:''' "If you ever harass Xikui again, I won't just eject you out of the Sky-Faring Commission, and I'll also flush you off Luofu."
::'''Xikui:''' Honestly, when I first cast my eyes on Madam Yukong, my heart skipped a beat.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have anything else to ask. See you next time.
