::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000085: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502011901.json-->
::'''Xikui:''' Management Strategy for Reporting Starskiff Traffic, check. Safety Inspection Guide, check. The life satisfaction survey for the new Outworlder batch, check. Documents are in order... now to confirm the schedule for the meeting.
::'''Xikui:''' Mm, there's still time. The relevant documentation for the Alchemy Commission's medicinal exports... requires confirmation from the person in charge. Also... souvenir bag orders for the merchant guilds should have arrived. I'll send someone to pick them up later.
::'''Xikui:''' Hmm? What is it, {{MC|f=young lady|m=young man}}? You've been staring at me for a while. How may I help you?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you busy with?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119005-->
:::'''Xikui:''' I am Madam Yukong's secretary, charged with handling much documentation... I won't go into detail about my job scope.
:::'''Xikui:''' You're not really interested in arranging work and poring over corporate files, are you?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I just thought you looked nice, is all.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119008-->
:::'''Xikui:''' Hahaha, I'll accept your compliment then.
:::'''Xikui:''' You know I am Madam Yukong's secretary, yes? Looking good is also part of my job in the Sky-Faring Commission.
:::'''Xikui:''' Haha, are you serious? I was just kidding.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not a {{MC|f=young lady|m=young man}}.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119012-->
:::'''Xikui:''' Hahaha, how cute.
:::'''Xikui:''' Well then, here's the first tip from the Chief Secretary of the Head of the Sky-Faring Commission: Don't ever judge a book by its cover on Xianzhou. Anyone you talk to could be hundreds of years old. That is the norm here.
:::'''Xikui:''' Also, second tip: When someone older than you speaks, it's best to just listen.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502119015-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119015-->
::'''Xikui:''' Hold on, I remember you. "An important guest of Xianzhou," "General Jing Yuan's appointed savior"... From the perspective of an insignificant secretary, you're a major character.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502011901_687-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502011901_687-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Oooh, am I really that important?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119017-->
:::'''Xikui:''' More than you think, I can assure you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} "General Jing Yuan's appointed savior"?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119019-->
:::'''Xikui:''' Oh, you don't believe me?
:::'''Xikui:''' I just made that up, this "savior" honorific. Though I'm sure that General Jing Yuan thinks so as well.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you up to, lavishing me with such praise?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119022-->
:::'''Xikui:''' Hmm? What am I up to? Just to make you like me, of course. I'm so cute, and you've got nothing to lose by returning the favor. Is that so surprising?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're a sight for sore eyes.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119024-->
::::'''Xikui:''' Oh, falling in love so quickly? I really must hand it to myself then.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not falling for this.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119026-->
::::'''Xikui:''' Falling? I don't know what you're talking about.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502119027-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502119027-->
::'''Xikui:''' All right, all right. I've got business to attend do. See that pile of work here? I still want to clock off work on time. It was fun teasing you, so here's a small gift for you.
::'''Xikui:''' If there's nothing else, I'm getting back to work.
