::<!--Trigger PerformanceD 404021303: Config/Level/Mission/4040213/Act/Act404021303.json-->
::'''Xikui:''' Yeah, I was so busy, I almost kicked myself in the face. All in a day's work at the Sky-Faring Commission! Time for the guilds' list to be updated once again...
::'''Xikui:''' So, if you're here to invite me out for tea or theater, forget it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Does it ever feel like someone here is slacking off?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021327-->
:::'''Xikui:''' Yeah. I mean, I only see you sauntering around as you do... Hang on, what's Yanming doing right now? He's staring daggers at us over here. Is he mad about something?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Shouldn't you hand over the guilds' list work to the guild to do themselves?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021329-->
:::'''Xikui:''' *sigh* It's common practice for our secretary to process all of this paperwork. The Amicassadors of all the guilds are tied down just from handling all of this year's materials...
:::'''Xikui:''' Hang on, what's Yanming doing right now? He's staring daggers at us over here. Is he mad about something?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404021331-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021331-->
::'''Xikui:''' Tsk, we're both working for the same Sky-Faring Commission, how is he able to slack off so openly?
::'''Xikui:''' Excuse me. I need to have a word with him.
::----
::You watch as the two of them start bickering, each ducking the other's questions &mdash; bringing up each other's backers, whispering about other colleagues' incompetence, shouting about an already oversaturated workload.
::Yanming finally breaks for pause, just as Xikui takes the chance to shove a pile of documents into Yanming's hands &mdash; as if piercing him straight through the heart with a rapier.
::At last, victory. Yanming is stunned, before he slinks away, dejected. The curtain falls on another trivial scene from the Palace of Astrum's millennia-old office drama.
::----
::<!--Custom String Trigger: YanmingZhanyong-->
