:::'''Xikui:''' A while ago, while tidying up my room, I found a book titled ''A Guide to Merchants and Mysteries'' in my bookshelf. Tingyun lent it to me, and I keep forgetting to return it to her all this time.
:::'''Xikui:''' I really hope that I would be able to personally return this book to her one day...
:;(If {{Mission|A New Venture on the Eighth Dawn (Trailblaze Mission)|showChapter=0}} has not been completed)
:::'''Xikui:''' Many are looking for her. As much as I want to find her, Madam Yukong doesn't allow me to do so.
:::'''Xikui:''' I guess it's because Madam Yukong doesn't want me to get as deeply involved in the matter as her, knowing how slim the chance of finding Tingyun is.
:::'''Xikui:''' Since that's the case, I can only stay by Madam Yukong's side and help her get through the trying times in my own way.
:::'''Xikui:''' Ahhh... I feel so bad and powerless. I can't help but feel small and insignificant when such emotions hit me...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
